<TABLE BORDER=0 cellpadding=4 border=0 cellspacing=1 WIDTH="95%"><TR bgcolor="#000000"><TD COLSPAN=2><CENTER><FONT SIZE="2" COLOR="#00ff00" FACE="Verdana, Arial">T O P I C  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; R E V I E W</font></CENTER></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#1f1f1f"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Lurker</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial"><BR>I love the way the Item Database is coming together with the new search capabilities.<P>There are a couple search criteria items that I would like to see added.  There should be a check box to show only Magical Items, and a check box to remove No Drop items.  There should also be a check box to filter out "junk" (anything worth less than 0.001pp)<P>The "Sort by" pulldown should have selections for Damage/Delay ratio, and AC/Weight ratios.<P>Search by name should also check the "Lore Text" for matches.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#1f1f1f"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Megaton</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Hi,<P>Thanks for the feedback. I'll see how far I can get implementing those great suggestions!<P>------------------<BR><A HREF="http://mailto:megaton@usa.net" TARGET=_blank>Megaton</A></FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#1f1f1f"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">fyredrake</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Another helpful search method would be the ability to search by the adds. like search for items that affect INT or DEX   etc.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#1f1f1f"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Megaton</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Hmm, searching by item stats are sort of implied when you do a 'sortby'.<P>I also implemented the above suggestions, keep them coming!  <IMG SRC="http://www.hackersquest.gomp.ch/ubb/smile.gif"></FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#1f1f1f"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Lurker</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial"><BR>Megaton, YOU ROCK!   <IMG SRC="http://www.hackersquest.gomp.ch/ubb/smile.gif">  It looks like all of those suggestions have been implemented... it makes the searches a lot more useful for me.<P>You might want to check out the "Bloody Mantle" (item 7110).  It shows up in the search results list as having an AC of -3.<P>Now what I would really like to see is additional information on the "showitem" page.  Pretty much all the extra info that used to show up on the old pages (before they went to this new system)... things like Item Size, Color, Proc Level, Light, Equip Slot, Weight Reduction, Container Slotsize.  It would also be nice to see Damage per second displayed for weapons, and the AC per stone displayed for armor.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#1f1f1f"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Darklight</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">The bloody mantle actually does have a negative AC. It's pretty much a quest item. There's a picture at Allakazam's under Shoulder Slot equipment.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#1f1f1f"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Lurker</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">If it really does have a negative AC then the problem is with the "showitem" screen... because it doesn't show any AC rating there at all.</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
</FONT>
